				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				One piece of advice, work on ALL of your slashing and blunt skills EARLY.  When you get to later levels it is much harder to build them up.  It's bad when you get an awesome one-hand blunt weapon and you've put all of your skill points in one-hand slash!
