			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Improving weapons skills later on IS hard, but not impossible.  The best way to do this is to get into a large group that won't mind you practicing.  Then you can use a fast low-damage weapon of the type you want to improve.  As long as what you are fighting cons at least blue to you, you'll improve skill fairly rapidly.<BR>

